{
  "stem": "7337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he refused to ever put a claim into-- he was not going to deal with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he said in principle he was not prepared to deal with Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When he died, I was an executor of his estate, together with a German Jewish lawyer.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we decided that it was foolish not to put in claims.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I never found his records of where his properties were situated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I knew some of the names.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were able through-- with the help of a German lawyer, after the war, to trace a number of properties.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And for those I got compensation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It can never be adequate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only for what they were worth?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, nothing like it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] The-- the values that they paid out were minimal compared to the real value.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they're doing it now with East Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I've got claims running in East Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] What claims are you-- what you got in East Germany?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's some real estate in East Germany that we were able to trace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got a judgement in 1962 from the West German courts, to prove that the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] price that the Nazis paid for that building, or those buildings, was exactly the amount of money of the tax that Jews had to pay in order to leave Germany-- and had no relation at all to the value of the buildings.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the court then gave me a ruling that this was an illegal sale, and I was to be refunded.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When East Germany joined with Germany, the laws in East Germany were withdrawn, and the West German laws applied.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So now the East German claims are being processed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hopefully.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
